Task
Changing the sign of each element in an array
Write a function called oppositeArray that takes the array arr as an argument and returns an array in which each element is replaced with the opposite element.
Example:
â€¢ function oppositeArray ([1, -2, 3]) must return [-1, 2, -3].

Solution
function oppositeArray (arr) {
 let newArr = [];
 for (let i = 0; i <arr.length; i ++) {
   newArr.push (arr [i] * (- 1))
 }
return newArr;
}
